# rmcp-verify project ontology — deliberately empty of individuals.
#
# rmcp-pack's own ontology.ttl (packs/rmcp-pack/ontology.ttl) is a complete,
# closed model of the rmcp:HandlerMethod (43), rmcp:Macro (7),
# rmcp:Transport (7), and rmcp:Feature (15) individuals; this consumer adds
# no project-specific facts on top of it (mirrors
# examples/star-toml-verify/schema/domain.ttl's and
# examples/praxis-core-verify/schema/domain.ttl's same posture). This file
# exists only to satisfy `[ontology] source` in ggen.toml — the real domain
# facts come entirely from the wired pack.

@prefix rmcp: <http://seanchatmangpt.github.io/packs/rmcp#> .
@prefix rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
